there were three little pigs.
And they all wanted to build their houses out of straw.

One pig built his house out of straw.
Another pig built his house out of clay.
And the third little pig made his house out of sticks.
Then a wolf came along and he said,
“Little pig, little pig, let me come in.”

The first little pig said, “Not by the hair on my chinny chin chin.
